extractedData.title: Life Insurance Policy
extractedData.summary: Term life insurance policy providing coverage for 10 years with beneficiaries listed as spouse and children.

suggestions: Set a reminder for policy renewal 60 days before expiration
You might want to add your children's guardian information

extractedData.title: Last Will and Testament
extractedData.summary: Legal will designating asset distribution and guardianship arrangements for minor children.

suggestions: Review your will every 3-5 years or after major life events
Ensure your executor has a copy of this document
Consider creating a living trust for additional asset protection

extractedData.title: Advance Healthcare Directive
extractedData.summary: Healthcare directive specifying medical treatment preferences and appointing healthcare proxy.

suggestions: Share this with your healthcare proxy and primary physician
Consider adding specific preferences for end-of-life care
Review and update if your health status changes significantly
